One Move Captures White (2)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to Play.\b0
\par White has just made an eye with white \'a1\'e2 in an attempt to live.
\par
\par White might think this move is successful in making life.
\par
\par However -
\par
\par Please strike the vital point and capture white beautifully.
\par }
