Diagram 3 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is the only move that captures white.
\par
\par This is also the 2-1 point.
\par
\par White must block at 2.
\par
\par Now, if black plays dansu at 3, white has no countermeasures left. White is dead.
\par
\par }
